# Water cluster, two-step Cholesky decomposition.
# Same physics as water_cluster_cholesky but pivoted CD is routed
# through three-center machinery (orbital-pair pivots on atom pairs;
# metric Cholesky factor; B = (mu nu | piv) M^{-1/2}).
# Cf. F. Folkestad, E. F. Kjonstad and H. Koch, J. Chem. Phys. 150,
# 194112 (2019). Exact at threshold; reproduces water_cluster_cholesky
# energies to within numerical precision.
System water_cluster.xyz
Method HF
Basis aug-cc-pVDZ
DensityFitting false
Cholesky true
CholeskyAlgorithm TwoStep
CholeskyThr 1e-7
IntegralThresh 1e-14



Logfile water_cluster_cholesky_twostep.log
SaveChk water_cluster_cholesky_twostep.chk
BasisRotate false
